Project Title:

Sales Prediction Using Python

Project Description

Sales Prediction Using Python is a machine learning project that predicts product sales based on advertising expenditures across different media platforms such as TV, Radio, and Newspaper. The project helps businesses estimate future sales and make informed marketing decisions.

Objective

The main objective of this project is to develop a machine learning model that can predict sales based on advertising budgets. This helps organizations optimize marketing strategies and improve business performance.

Technologies Used
Python
Pandas
NumPy
Matplotlib
Seaborn
Scikit-learn
Jupyter Notebook
Dataset

The dataset contains advertising information and corresponding sales values. The main attributes include:

TV Advertising Budget
Radio Advertising Budget
Newspaper Advertising Budget
Sales
Project Workflow
Import required libraries.
Load the dataset.
Explore and analyze the data.
Check for missing values.
Select features and target variables.
Split the dataset into training and testing sets.
Train the Linear Regression model.
Predict sales values.
Evaluate model performance.
Visualize the results.
Machine Learning Algorithm

Linear Regression

Linear Regression is used to find the relationship between advertising expenditure and sales, allowing the prediction of future sales values.

Features
Data preprocessing and analysis.
Sales prediction using machine learning.
Model evaluation using R² Score and Mean Absolute Error.
Data visualization for better understanding.
Results

The model successfully predicts sales based on advertising budgets. The predicted results can help businesses make better marketing and financial decisions.

Applications
Sales Forecasting
Marketing Budget Planning
Business Analytics
Revenue Prediction
Advertising Strategy Optimization
Conclusion

This project demonstrates the use of machine learning techniques to predict sales using advertising data. By analyzing historical marketing expenditures and sales performance, businesses can forecast future sales, optimize advertising investments, and improve overall decision-making processes.
